fields.name: GB (Great Britain) - Environment Department
fields.comments:
Scraping via normal GET request, Pagination via GET param.
- Reset session cookie manually before starting scraper runs (cookie stays valid a couple of days)
- Manually press 'search' button once within search form on website

Num pages: 9.649 (192.965 / 20), 2016-01-21

fields.name: IE (Ireland) - Agriculture Department
fields.comments:
1. Go to https://publicapps.agriculture.gov.ie/capben/cap_ben_master.jsp, confirm your no-robot status, confirm terms
2. Go to year, do one first search, use cookie for scraping
3. Scrape per Location by manually inserting the Locations into the POST form data of the Request Page Type AND adopt region for ScraperElem manually on every region change
5. Divide viewing results by 15 (entries per page) and adopt the range function for pagination
6. Start scraping (move every scraper JSON file to a separate file for later concatenation!)

GENERAL: Extremely short session period (< 15 min), start scraping process instantly!!!
